  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to substantiate prediction accuracy(with a tighter 95%
      confidence interval compared to current diagnostic modalities), of a lung cancer biomarker
      for risk stratification of patients into high and low risk categories to aid in clinical
      evaluation of the patient.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
